      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of superlative caliber, this specimen represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains entirely free of discernible wear. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that is indistinguishable from its initial delivery. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the individual who demands peak aesthetic and mechanical refinement without exception.",
