    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that can only be described as a showroom-quality masterpiece. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did on the delivery floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with no stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are free of any curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with no signs of creasing, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. All electronic systems, from the high-fidelity audio to the dual-zone climate control, function with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the top side. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
